en_219487_0	The buttala police have shot at an individual who ran over a police officer and  fled the scene while riding a motorcycle intoxicated in the Buttala city.
en_219487_1	Police noted that owing to the shooting, the suspect had sustained injuries in his leg, and he has been admitted to the Sirigala hospital for treatment.
en_219487_2	The incident occurred when the suspect and another individual were traveling on a motorcycle in the Buttala city last evening.
en_219487_3	However police noted that the police officer was not harmed due to the incident.
